e":"2020-04-22T11:13:05.000Z","msg":"我阿爸嘅祖先係鄂圖曼帝國嘅人"},{"pid":"83a9fa6d8894eb642c196636fb833251c47bb02c","tid":1984244,"uid":144628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:13:41.000Z","msg":"其實只要你同香港人理念一致 你就係香港人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5630f69e17c3fb62ecb52e7529aff7a8b020e6","tid":1984244,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83a9fa6d8894eb642c196636fb833251c47bb02c","tid":1984244,"uid":144628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:13:41.000Z","msg":"其實只要你同香港人理念一致 你就係香港人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:15:16.000Z","msg":"一直都係，但係要認清香港就係香港"},{"pid":"79064a8743368fa57722e5ba73b2a48434506b79","tid":1984244,"uid":238660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c726d910eef208c95c2e37612eab594d5eb413c1","tid":1984244,"uid":205927,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:09:00.000Z","msg":"其實咩血統都冇咩所謂，最重要係個理念"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:17:31.000Z","msg":"編文最主要係講緊我哋唔係支那族"},{"pid":"1d0d668dd5d08defd9abc53b4a0deda932f58771","tid":1984244,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"278edb84d61c409ecdc9253e439068ca3ac1cd28","tid":1984244,"uid":310793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:12:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌! 我推唔撚到呀!</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:17:41.000Z","msg":"幫你"},{"pid":"4f78802141858ba56263dbb17149a83205f4a42a","tid":1984244,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:24:21.000Z","msg":"我唔係支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"532852b35d31ff330a46b301b33c5f00e51aee6f","tid":1984244,"uid":259674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:27:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d29352ffe6cda11888ad3193974129b48b